tspan.tspan: Each of these individuals held a unique place in our hearts, their
contributions to our college community immeasurable. Their talents
and versatility enriched our collective experience, creating memories
that stand as a testament to their impact. Though these individuals
may have departed from the world we know, they will forever stay
in our hearts. Their heartbeats may have ceased, but the rhythm of
their presence resonates in the decibel of our ears. They did not
deserve this fate, yet wherever they are, we believe they continue to

text.tspan: be a source of support for us.

tspan.tspan: In this journey of healing, let us stand together, supporting one
another with love, harmony, and peace. Our unity can act as
unparalleled strength, gradually filling the void left by our departed
As we honor their memory, let us focus on moving forward together,
embracing the opportunity for unity, compassion, and
understanding. Resilience as a community will be our guiding force,

text.tspan: fostering an environment of healing and mutual support.

tspan.tspan: The pages of this magazine serve as a tribute to the strength of our
community, demonstrating resilience even in the face of adversity.

Honoring Our Beloved
Footprints
This year has been a somber chapter for us as we mourn the loss of
cherished individuals from our college. The stampede, claiming
precious lives, has etched an indelible mark in our hearts that no
nectar of love can erase. Though those pulchritudinous souls have
left a void, their faces will forever be our strength, akin to guardian
angels watching over us. The inadequacy of words to express the
pain and shock felt by their loved ones is profound. No medicine can
heal their wounds, and no tissue can absorb their tears. We extend
our heartfelt condolences to those who are grieving, wishing the
Almighty to provide them with the strengthto endure this
unimaginable loss.
